  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <lg xml:id="TolC267">
          <l>anti lāṅka vacainilaik kiḷaviyeṉ</l>
          <l>ṟāyira ṇṭāku miyaṟkait teṉpa.</l>
        </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/165/mode/1up">165</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ituvum tattaṅ kuṟippiṟ poruḷ ceykuvaṉavaṟṟaiyum acainilaiyaiyum uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
varalāṟu:
      </p>
      <p>
iṭañcuṭṭi vantatu:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC267-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘varumē, cēyiḻai yantiṟ koḻunaṟ kāṇiya’</l>
        <trailer>[kuṟun – 293]</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa varum.
      </p>
      <p>
acainilai:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC267-Ilam-cit2">
        <l>‘antil kacciṉaṉ kaḻaliṉaṉ’</l>
        <trailer>[akam – 76]</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa varum.  (19)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n215/mode/1up">212</ref>.</p>
      <p>
i – ḷ. antileṉṉuñcol, āṅkeṉṉum iṭapporu ḷuṇarttuvatum, acainilaiyumeṉa iraṇṭām. e–ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u – m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC267-Cena-cit1">
        <l>‘varumē ― cēyiḻai yantiṟ koḻunaṟ kāṇiya’<app><note>kuṟun. 293</note></app></l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpuḻi āṅku varumeṉṟavāṟām.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC267-Cena-cit2">
        <l>‘antiṟ kacciṉaṉ kaḻaliṉaṉ’<app><note>(akam. 76)</note></app></l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa vāḷātē acaittu niṉṟatu.	(19)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/296/mode/1up">296</ref>.</p>
      <p>
itu, poruḷpaṭumāṟum acainilaiyuṅ kūṟukiṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <p>
(i–ḷ) antilāṅkavacainilaik kiḷaviyeṉ ṟāyiraṇṭāku miyaṟkkait teṉpa ― anti leṉṉuñcol lāṅka veṉṉu miṭapporuḷuṇarttutalu macainilaic collātalumeṉṉumav viraṇṭu kūṟā miyaṟkaiyai yuṭaitteṉṟu kūṟuvar pulavareṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
(u–m)
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC267-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>‘varumē cēyiḻai yantil’</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC267-Nacc-cit2">
        <l>‘antil kacciṉaṉ kaḻaliṉaṉ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa iṭamu macainilaiyumāy niṉṟatu.  <num xml:lang="en">(19)</num>
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n182/mode/1up">175</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ituvumatu.
      </p>
      <p>
i–ḷ.: ― antil eṉpatu āṅku eṉṉum poruṇmai peṟṟum, acainilaiyākiyum varum. e–ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u–m ―
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC267-Tey-cit1">
        <l>varumē cēyiḻai yantiṟ-koḻunaṟ kāṇiya<note place="foot">kuṟuṅ. 293.</note></l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu āṅkeṉṉum poruḷuṇarttiṟṟu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC267-Tey-cit2">
        <l>antiṟ kacciṉaṉ kaḻaliṉaṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
(akam. 76) eṉpuḻi, acainilaiyāyiṟṟu.	[19]
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
